{"word":"G2621 - κατάκειμαι - katákeimai - kat-ak'-i-mahee - Keep","slug":"G2621","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατάκειμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katákeimai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-ak'-i-mahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Keep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - katakeimai</b> - <i>kat-ak'-i-mahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>; to <i>lie down</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>be sick</i>; specifically to <i>recline</i> at a meal: - keep, lie, sit at meat (down)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1945\">G1945</a>, <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>, <a href=\"#/G345\">G345</a>, <a href=\"#/G3873\">G3873</a>, <a href=\"#/G4029\">G4029</a>, <a href=\"#/G4295\">G4295</a>, <a href=\"#/G480\">G480</a>, <a href=\"#/G4873\">G4873</a>, <a href=\"#/G606\">G606</a>"}]}